{
  "id": null,
  "panels": [
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "panels": [],
      "title": "Connector Health",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "description": "```\nonyx_index_attempts_active\n```\n\nCurrent indexing attempts by status (in_progress, not_started) and connector. Shows what the system is actively working on.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 50,
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "stacking": {
              "mode": "normal"
            }
          },
          "unit": "short"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 1
      },
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": [
            "last"
          ],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "onyx_index_attempts_active{tenant_id=~\"$tenant_id\", source=~\"$source\", connector_name=~\"$connector_name\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{status}} / {{source}} / {{connector_name}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Active Index Attempts",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "description": "```\nsum by (status) (onyx_connectors_by_status)\n```\n\nDistribution of all connectors by their current status (Active, Paused, etc.).",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          }
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 1
      },
      "id": 11,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": [
            "last"
          ],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "right"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (status) (onyx_connectors_by_status{tenant_id=~\"$tenant_id\"})",
          "legendFormat": "{{status}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Connectors by Status",
      "type": "piechart"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "description": "```\nsum(onyx_connectors_in_error_total)\n```\n\nTotal count of connectors currently in a repeated error state. Yellow at 1+, red at 5+.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 1
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 5
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 18,
        "y": 1
      },
      "id": 13,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "textMode": "value_and_name"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(onyx_connectors_in_error_total{tenant_id=~\"$tenant_id\"})",
          "legendFormat": "Errors",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Connectors in Error Total",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "description": "```\ntopk(20, onyx_connector_last_success_age_seconds)\n```\n\nTime since each connector last completed a successful index. Red = stale (>1 day), Yellow = warning (>1 hour), Green = fresh. Updates after each successful indexing run.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {},
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "Staleness (sec)"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "unit",
                "value": "s"
              },
              {
                "id": "thresholds",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "absolute",
                  "steps": [
                    {
                      "color": "green",
                      "value": null
                    },
                    {
                      "color": "yellow",
                      "value": 3600
                    },
                    {
                      "color": "red",
                      "value": 86400
                    }
                  ]
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "custom.cellOptions",
                "value": {
                  "type": "color-background"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 12,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 9
      },
      "id": 9,
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "topk(20, onyx_connector_last_success_age_seconds{tenant_id=~\"$tenant_id\", source=~\"$source\", connector_name=~\"$connector_name\"})",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Connector Staleness (seconds since last success)",
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": {
              "Time": true,
              "__name__": true,
              "cc_pair_id": true,
              "instance": true,
              "job": true
            },
            "renameByName": {
              "Value": "Staleness (sec)",
              "connector_name": "Connector",
              "source": "Source",
              "tenant_id": "Tenant"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "sortBy",
          "options": {
            "fields": {},
            "sort": [
              {
                "desc": true,
                "field": "Staleness (sec)"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "type": "table"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "description": "```\nonyx_connector_in_error_state == 1\n```\n\nConnectors that have failed repeatedly and entered an error state. These need manual attention.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {}
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 10,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 21
      },
      "id": 10,
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "onyx_connector_in_error_state{tenant_id=~\"$tenant_id\", source=~\"$source\", connector_name=~\"$connector_name\"} == 1",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Connectors in Error State",
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": {
              "Time": true,
              "Value": true,
              "__name__": true,
              "cc_pair_id": true,
              "instance": true,
              "job": true
            },
            "renameByName": {
              "connector_name": "Connector",
              "source": "Source",
              "tenant_id": "Tenant"
            }
          }
        }
      ],
      "type": "table"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "description": "```\nA: onyx_connector_docs_indexed\nB: onyx_connector_error_count\n```\n\nTotal documents indexed (90-day rolling sum of successful attempts) and total failed index attempts for each connector.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {},
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "Failed Attempts"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "thresholds",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "absolute",
                  "steps": [
                    {
                      "color": "green",
                      "value": null
                    },
                    {
                      "color": "yellow",
                      "value": 1
                    },
                    {
                      "color": "red",
                      "value": 5
                    }
                  ]
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "custom.cellOptions",
                "value": {
                  "type": "color-background"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 10,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 31
      },
      "id": 15,
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "onyx_connector_docs_indexed{tenant_id=~\"$tenant_id\", source=~\"$source\", connector_name=~\"$connector_name\"}",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "onyx_connector_error_count{tenant_id=~\"$tenant_id\", source=~\"$source\", connector_name=~\"$connector_name\"}",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Docs Indexed & Failed Attempts per Connector",
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "merge",
          "options": {}
        },
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": {
              "Time": true,
              "__name__": true,
              "cc_pair_id": true,
              "instance": true,
              "job": true,
              "tenant_id": true
            },
            "renameByName": {
              "Value #A": "Docs Indexed",
              "Value #B": "Failed Attempts",
              "connector_name": "Connector",
              "source": "Source"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "sortBy",
          "options": {
            "fields": {},
            "sort": [
              {
                "desc": true,
                "field": "Failed Attempts"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "type": "table"
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 41
      },
      "panels": [],
      "title": "Indexing Pipeline",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "description": "```\nsum by (source, outcome) (rate(onyx_indexing_task_completed_total[5m])) * 60\n```\n\nRate of completed indexing tasks per minute on docfetching and docprocessing workers, broken down by source type and outcome (success/failure).",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineWidth": 2
          },
          "unit": "short"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 42
      },
      "id": 5,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": [
            "last"
          ],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (source, outcome) (rate(onyx_indexing_task_completed_total{source=~\"$source\", tenant_id=~\"$tenant_id\"}[5m])) * 60",
          "legendFormat": "{{source}} ({{outcome}})",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Indexing Task Throughput (tasks/min)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "description": "```\np95: histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (source, le) (rate(onyx_indexing_task_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])))\np50: histogram_quantile(0.50, ...)\n```\n\nHow long indexing tasks take to complete. p95 = worst-case (95th percentile), p50 = typical (median). Use to identify slow connector types.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 5,
            "lineWidth": 2
          },
          "unit": "s"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 42
      },
      "id": 6,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": [
            "last"
          ],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (source, le) (rate(onyx_indexing_task_duration_seconds_bucket{source=~\"$source\", tenant_id=~\"$tenant_id\"}[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "p95 {{source}}",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum by (source, le) (rate(onyx_indexing_task_duration_seconds_bucket{source=~\"$source\", tenant_id=~\"$tenant_id\"}[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "p50 {{source}}",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Task Duration p95 / p50",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "description": "```\nsum by (source, connector_name, outcome) (rate(onyx_indexing_task_completed_total[5m])) * 60\n```\n\nCompleted indexing tasks per minute broken down by individual connector and outcome. Use to compare throughput across connectors.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineWidth": 2
          },
          "unit": "short"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 50
      },
      "id": 7,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": [
            "last"
          ],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (source, connector_name, outcome) (rate(onyx_indexing_task_completed_total{source=~\"$source\", tenant_id=~\"$tenant_id\", connector_name=~\"$connector_name\"}[5m])) * 60",
          "legendFormat": "{{source}} / {{connector_name}} ({{outcome}})",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Indexing Tasks by Connector Source",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "description": "```\nhistogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (source, connector_name, le) (rate(onyx_indexing_task_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])))\n```\n\n95th percentile indexing task duration per connector. Shows which specific connectors are slowest to index.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 5,
            "lineWidth": 2
          },
          "unit": "s"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 50
      },
      "id": 8,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": [
            "last"
          ],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (source, connector_name, le) (rate(onyx_indexing_task_duration_seconds_bucket{source=~\"$source\", tenant_id=~\"$tenant_id\", connector_name=~\"$connector_name\"}[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "p95 {{source}} / {{connector_name}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Indexing Duration by Source (p95)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "description": "```\nsum(increase(onyx_indexing_task_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le)\n```\n\nDistribution of task execution times. Color intensity shows how many tasks fell into each duration bucket. Reveals bimodal distributions and outliers.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "scaleDistribution": {
              "log": 2,
              "type": "log"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 58
      },
      "id": 22,
      "options": {
        "calculate": false,
        "cellGap": 1,
        "color": {
          "mode": "scheme",
          "scheme": "Oranges"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "show": true,
          "yHistogram": true
        },
        "yAxis": {
          "unit": "s"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(increase(onyx_indexing_task_duration_seconds_bucket{source=~\"$source\", tenant_id=~\"$tenant_id\"}[5m])) by (le)",
          "format": "heatmap",
          "legendFormat": "{{le}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Task Runtime Heatmap",
      "type": "heatmap"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "description": "```\nA: rate(onyx_celery_task_retried_total[5m]) * 60\nB: rate(onyx_celery_task_revoked_total[5m]) * 60\nC: rate(onyx_celery_task_rejected_total[5m]) * 60\n```\n\nRate of task retries, revocations, and rejections per minute. Retries indicate transient failures. Revocations indicate cancelled tasks. Rejections indicate worker refusals.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineWidth": 2
          },
          "unit": "short"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 58
      },
      "id": 21,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": [
            "last"
          ],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "noValue": "No events (healthy)",
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "rate(onyx_celery_task_retried_total[5m]) * 60",
          "legendFormat": "retry: {{task_name}}",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "rate(onyx_celery_task_revoked_total[5m]) * 60",
          "legendFormat": "revoked: {{task_name}}",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "expr": "rate(onyx_celery_task_rejected_total[5m]) * 60",
          "legendFormat": "rejected: {{task_name}}",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Task Retries & Revocations",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 66
      },
      "panels": [],
      "title": "Queue Infrastructure",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "description": "```\nonyx_queue_depth\n```\n\nNumber of tasks waiting in each Celery queue. High values indicate workers can't keep up with incoming work. Covers all 20 queue types.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "stacking": {
              "mode": "none"
            }
          },
          "unit": "short"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 67
      },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": [
            "last"
          ],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "onyx_queue_depth",
          "legendFormat": "{{queue}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Queue Depths",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "description": "```\nderiv(onyx_queue_depth[5m]) * 60\n```\n\nRate of change of queue depth per minute. Positive = queue growing (tasks arriving faster than consumed). Negative = queue draining. Zero = stable.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "thresholdsStyle": {
              "mode": "line"
            }
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 0
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 10
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 100
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 67
      },
      "id": 16,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": [
            "last"
          ],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "deriv(onyx_queue_depth[5m]) * 60",
          "legendFormat": "{{queue}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Queue Growth Rate (tasks/min)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "description": "```\nonyx_queue_oldest_task_age_seconds > 0\n```\n\nAge of the oldest waiting task in each non-empty queue. High values indicate stuck or starved queues. Only shows queues with items.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineWidth": 2
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 60
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 300
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "s"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 75
      },
      "id": 17,
      "options": {
